import React from 'react';
import { PortHead } from './components/header';
import {
	Main,
	Place,
	Tall,
	StaTall,
	StaLand,
	Flex,
	Land,
	Spacer,
	BoxT,
	StaLandV,
} from './components/components';
import { NavLink } from 'react-router-dom';

export const Portfolio = () => (
	<main>
		<PortHead />
		<Spacer h="h4" />
		<Main>
			<Land
				to="/progetti/yape"
				container="w-70 center w-100-m"
				article="dim"
				background="./img/lima/4.png"
				title="Metro de Lima"
				group="segnaletica"
			/>
			<Spacer h="h6 h3-m" />
			<Flex width="w-100" class="flex-column-m justify-between">
				<Tall
					to="/progetti/yape"
					container="w-45 mr3 mr0-m w-70-m center-m"
					article="dim ba b--silver"
					background="./img/yape.png"
					title="Yape"
					group="immagine coordinata"
				/>
				<Flex width="w-40 w-100-m" class="flex-column justify-between mt7 mt6-m">
					<Land
						to="/progetti/yape"
						container="w-100-m mb3"
						article="dim"
						background="./img/corte/corte.png"
						title="Corte d'Arte"
						group="immagine coordinata"
					/>

					<StaTall
						to="/progetti/yape"
						container="w-100-m"
						article="dim"
						background="/img/corte/posters/poster.png"
						title="Corte d'Arte"
						group="poster"
					/>
				</Flex>
			</Flex>
			<Spacer h="h4 h3-m" />
			<StaLandV
				container="center w-70 w-100-m"
				background="./img/ducati.mp4"
				title="Sempre più a contatto con la tua Ducati"
				group="video • in collaborazione con e-Novia"
			/>
			<Spacer h="h4 h3-m" />
			<Tall
					to="/progetti/yape"
					container="w-45 mr3 mr0-m w-70-m center-m"
					article="dim ba b--silver"
					background="./img/yape.png"
					title="Yape"
					group="immagine coordinata"
				/>
			<BoxT title="posters">

			</BoxT>
		</Main>
	</main>
);
